"title": "7742: missionaries, support for",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7742",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Though facing hardships, missionaries receive strength from God to enable them to carry out their task. They are entitled, too, to receive support, encouragement and financial assistance from other believers.</p>\n<h2>Missionaries face hardships</h2>\n<h3>Physical and emotional stress</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:17-Matt10:23\">MAT 10:17–10:23</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:11-Mark13:13\">MRK 13:11–13:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:12-Luke21:19\">LUK 21:12–21:19</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:5\">2CO 7:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:36\">ROM 8:35–8:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:11-2Cor4:13\">2CO 4:11–4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:3-2Cor6:5\">2CO 6:3–6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:8-2Cor6:10\">2CO 6:8–6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23-2Cor11:29\">2CO 11:23–11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:12\">PHP 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>Opposition to the message</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:9\">1CO 16:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:17-Acts4:18\">ACT 4:17–4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:9\">ACT 6:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:6-Acts13:8\">ACT 13:6–13:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:2\">1TH 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Missionaries strengthened by God</h2>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit gives power to witness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:21-John20:22\">JHN 20:21–20:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:49\">LUK 24:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:18-Rom15:19\">ROM 15:18–15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4-1Cor2:5\">1CO 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ promises his presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:20\">MAT 28:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:20\">MRK 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:10\">ACT 18:10</a></p>\n<h2>Missionaries supported by the church</h2>\n<h3>Missionaries supported by the sending church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:26\">ACT 14:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:3\">ACT 13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:40\">ACT 15:40</a></p>\n<h3>Missionaries supported by believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:27\">ACT 18:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:24\">ROM 15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:23-2Cor8:24\">2CO 8:23–8:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:13\">TIT 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Missionary work supported by church leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:14\">ACT 8:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:22-Acts11:23\">ACT 11:22–11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:30-Acts15:32\">ACT 15:30–15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:7-Gal2:9\">GAL 2:7–2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Missionaries given financial support</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:14-Phil4:18\">PHP 4:14–4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:25\">PHP 2:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:11-1Cor9:14\">1CO 9:11–9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:5-1Cor16:6\">1CO 16:5–16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:6\">GAL 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:6-1Thess2:8\">1TH 2:6–2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Missionaries supported in prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:3\">COL 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:19-Eph6:20\">EPH 6:19–6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:19\">PHP 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:25\">1TH 5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:1\">2TH 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>Missionaries encouraged by visits and news</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:15\">ACT 28:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:19\">PHP 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:9-2Tim4:11\">2TI 4:9–4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:12\">TIT 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:12-Phlm1:13\">PHM 1:12–1:13</a></p>",
